  "data": {
    "title": "Envato Elements 2024: New AI Tools & Unlimited Creative Assets",
    "excerpt": "Envato Elements just leveled up with AI video, image, and audio tools. See the new features that make this $16.50/mo subscription a creative powerhouse.",
    "featured_image": {
      "$media": {
        "url": "https://tonyciencia.com/blog/envato-elements-new-features.jpg",
        "alt": "Envato Elements 2024: New AI Tools & Unlimited Creative Assets",
        "filename": "envato-elements-new-features.jpg"
      }
    },
    "content": [
      {
        "_type": "block",
        "style": "normal",
        "markDefs": [],
        "children": [
          {
            "_type": "span",
            "text": "If you work in content creation, design, or marketing, you already know the pain: you need a specific stock clip, a polished video template, or a fresh font, and suddenly you're burning $30 on a single download. Multiply that by dozens of assets per month, and your \"resource budget\" spirals out of control.",
            "marks": []
          }
        ]
      },
      {
        "_type": "block",
        "style": "normal",
        "markDefs": [],
        "children": [
          {
            "_type": "span",
            "text": "Envato Elements has been quietly solving this problem for years with unlimited downloads from a massive library. But their latest updates? They've shifted from \"useful subscription\" to \"indispensable creative toolkit.\"",
            "marks": []
          }
        ]
      },
      {
        "_type": "block",
        "style": "normal",
        "markDefs": [],
        "children": [
          {
            "_type": "span",
            "text": "I spent the last few weeks digging into every new feature. Here's what's changed, why it matters, and whether Envato Elements deserves a permanent spot in your workflow.",
            "marks": []
          }
        ]
      },
      {
        "_type": "block",
        "style": "normal",
        "markDefs": [],
        "children": [
          {
            "_type": "span",
            "text": "---",
            "marks": []
          }
        ]
      },
      {
        "_type": "block",
        "style": "h2",
        "markDefs": [],
        "children": [
          {
            "_type": "span",
            "text": "What Is Envato Elements in 2024?",
            "marks": []
          }
        ]
      },
      {
        "_type": "block",
        "style": "normal",
        "markDefs": [
          {
            "_key": "l0",
            "_type": "link",
            "href": "https://tonyciencia.com/en/posts/what-is-envato-elements"
          }
        ],
        "children": [
          {
            "_type": "span",
            "text": "Envato Elements",
            "marks": [
              "l0"
            ]
          },
          {
            "_type": "span",
            "text": " is an all-in-one creative asset subscription. Think of it as a buffet for professionals who need stock video, photos, music, sound effects, design templates, graphics, 3D assets, fonts, and add-ons — all under one flat monthly fee.",
            "marks": []
          }
        ]
      },
      {
        "_type": "block",
        "style": "normal",
        "markDefs": [],
        "children": [
          {
            "_type": "span",
            "text": "The numbers are staggering: ",
            "marks": []
          },
          {
            "_type": "span",
            "text": "28+ million creative assets",
            "marks": [
              "strong"
            ]
          },
          {
            "_type": "span",
            "text": " available for unlimited downloads. No per-asset pricing. No credits. No nickel-and-diming.",
            "marks": []
          }
        ]
      },
      {
        "_type": "block",
        "style": "normal",
        "markDefs": [],
        "children": [
          {
            "_type": "span",
            "text": "But the real story in 2024 is the addition of a full ",
            "marks": []
          },
          {
            "_type": "span",
            "text": "AI toolkit",
            "marks": [
              "strong"
            ]
          },
          {
            "_type": "span",
            "text": " that now ships with every subscription tier. We'll get into that shortly.",
            "marks": []
          }
        ]
      },
      {
        "_type": "block",
        "style": "normal",
        "markDefs": [
          {
            "_key": "l1",
            "_type": "link",
            "href": "https://tonyciencia.com/en/posts/what-is-envato-elements"
          }
