          {
            "_type": "span",
            "text": "New Features That Change the Game",
            "marks": []
          }
        ]
      },
      {
        "_type": "block",
        "style": "normal",
        "markDefs": [],
        "children": [
          {
            "_type": "span",
            "text": "Envato didn't just add a handful of tweaks — they rolled out a suite of capabilities that fundamentally expand what you can do inside the platform. Here are the standouts:",
            "marks": []
          }
        ]
      },
      {
        "_type": "block",
        "style": "h3",
        "markDefs": [],
        "children": [
          {
            "_type": "span",
            "text": "AI Image Generation & Editing",
            "marks": []
          }
        ]
      },
      {
        "_type": "block",
        "style": "normal",
        "markDefs": [],
        "children": [
          {
            "_type": "span",
            "text": "You can now generate custom images directly inside Envato Elements using AI. Need a hero image for a landing page with a very specific vibe? Type a prompt, refine it, and download. The editing tools let you tweak outputs without leaving the platform.",
            "marks": []
          }
        ]
      },
      {
        "_type": "block",
        "style": "normal",
        "markDefs": [],
        "children": [
          {
            "_type": "span",
            "text": "This alone saves you the hassle of jumping between a stock library and a separate AI image tool like Midjourney or DALL·E.",
            "marks": []
          }
        ]
      },
      {
        "_type": "block",
        "style": "h3",
        "markDefs": [],
        "children": [
          {
            "_type": "span",
            "text": "AI Video Generation & Editing",
            "marks": []
          }
        ]
      },
      {
        "_type": "block",
        "style": "normal",
        "markDefs": [],
        "children": [
          {
            "_type": "span",
            "text": "This one surprised me. Envato Elements now includes ",
            "marks": []
          },
          {
            "_type": "span",
            "text": "AI-powered video generation and editing",
            "marks": [
              "strong"
            ]
          },
          {
            "_type": "span",
            "text": ". You can create short video clips from text prompts and edit existing footage with AI-assisted tools. For social media creators pumping out Reels, TikToks, or YouTube Shorts, this is a massive time-saver.",
            "marks": []
          }
        ]
      },
      {
        "_type": "block",
        "style": "h3",
        "markDefs": [],
        "children": [
          {
            "_type": "span",
            "text": "AI Voice Over",
            "marks": []
          }
        ]
      },
      {
        "_type": "block",
        "style": "normal",
        "markDefs": [],
        "children": [
          {
            "_type": "span",
            "text": "Need a voiceover for a promo video or explainer? The new AI voiceover tool generates natural-sounding narration from your script. No microphone, no recording booth, no retakes.",
            "marks": []
          }
        ]
      },
      {
        "_type": "block",
        "style": "normal",
        "markDefs": [
          {
            "_key": "l2",
            "_type": "link",
            "href": "https://tonyciencia.com/en/posts/how-to-use-elevenlabs"
