      {
        "_type": "block",
        "style": "h3",
        "markDefs": [],
        "children": [
          {
            "_type": "span",
            "text": "AI Music & Sound Effects Generation",
            "marks": []
          }
        ]
      },
      {
        "_type": "block",
        "style": "normal",
        "markDefs": [],
        "children": [
          {
            "_type": "span",
            "text": "Royalty-free music libraries are great, but sometimes you need something *exact*. The new AI music generator lets you create custom tracks by specifying mood, tempo, and style. Same goes for sound effects.",
            "marks": []
          }
        ]
      },
      {
        "_type": "block",
        "style": "normal",
        "markDefs": [],
        "children": [
          {
            "_type": "span",
            "text": "Already have 340,000+ royalty-free music tracks and 940,000+ sound effects in the library? Yes. But having the option to generate something unique when nothing in the catalog fits is a creative safety net I didn't know I needed.",
            "marks": []
          }
        ]
      },
      {
        "_type": "block",
        "style": "h3",
        "markDefs": [],
        "children": [
          {
            "_type": "span",
            "text": "AI Graphics & Mockup Generation",
            "marks": []
          }
        ]
      },
      {
        "_type": "block",
        "style": "normal",
        "markDefs": [],
        "children": [
          {
            "_type": "span",
            "text": "Designers, this one's for you. Generate custom graphics, icons, and mockups using AI. Need a product mockup with a specific angle and lighting? Describe it and let the tool build it.",
            "marks": []
          }
        ]
      },
