          }
        ]
      },
      {
        "_type": "block",
        "style": "normal",
        "markDefs": [],
        "children": [
          {
            "_type": "span",
            "text": "The AI tools are genuinely useful, not gimmicky.",
            "marks": [
              "strong"
            ]
          },
          {
            "_type": "span",
            "text": " I've seen platforms bolt on AI features that feel like afterthoughts. Envato's AI toolkit is integrated cleanly. The image generator produces results competitive with standalone tools. The voiceover quality surprised me — it's usable for client work, not just internal drafts.",
            "marks": []
          }
