              "strong"
            ]
          },
          {
            "_type": "span",
            "text": " Every asset you download — stock footage, templates, AI-generated images — comes with lifetime commercial rights. No attribution required. No worrying about license expiry. For anyone producing client deliverables, this removes a huge source of legal anxiety.",
