      {
        "_type": "block",
        "style": "normal",
        "markDefs": [],
        "children": [
          {
            "_type": "span",
            "text": "Every Envato Elements subscription includes unlimited downloads of 28+ million creative assets — stock video, photos, music, sound effects, design templates, graphics, 3D assets, fonts, and add-ons. It also includes AI tools for image generation, video generation, voiceover, music creation, and graphics generation, plus a lifetime commercial license for everything you download.",
